<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>352</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Mi a khetden u chuh en un hinna a um,
 Tu zieng hin nang din hinna a um;
 Thing chunga Mi a khetden u chu en un,
 Migilo haw, Hukdam in um un.

[V2]
 En un hing un lau!
 Mi a khetden uchuh en un hinna a um,
 Tu zieng hin nang din hinna a um!

[V3]
 2. Bang zieka Isu'n gitlohna A puok A him?
 Nang git loh puo A hih loh ngal chun?
 Bang zieka A naka thienna thisan luong?
 A thihnan na bat a dit loh chun?

[V4]
 3. Na kisikna mitthi leh pauchamna ei puoi,
 A thisan ahi, thagau tandawk;
 Nang dinga A thisan lul piepa chungah,
 Kintak in na gitloh gikpuok nga'n.

[V5]
 4. Pathien in, A hun lawp ding thu chu ginglah kin,
 Thildang sep beh ding um ta puo'n a;
 Khawvel tawp tieng leh hung kilang kit intin,
 A nasep pat chuh sem zo ta'n a.

[V6]
 5. Lawp takin Lal Isu apatin la mengin,
 Kumsawt hinna nang A hun piek chuh;
 Thi kit ta-lo ding na hi tih kihen la,
 Na dikna Isu A hin ziekin.</lyrics>
<title>THERE IS LIFE FOR A LOOK</title>
</song>